  <h3>
    <a href="/p/whonix/featureblog/2013/03/in-depth-detailed-technical-whonix-design/">In depth, Detailed Technical Whonix Design</a>
  </h3>
  <div class="markdown_content"><p>Ever wanted to know what each and every file in Whonix Source Code is good for? It's now all documented.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/wiki/Design-Shared/">https://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/wiki/Design-Shared/</a></li>
<li><a href="https://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/wiki/Design-Gateway/">https://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/wiki/Design-Gateway/</a></li>
<li><a href="https://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/wiki/Design-Workstation/">https://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/wiki/Design-Workstation/</a></li>
</ul>
<p>The "old", more textual Whonix Design <a href="https://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/wiki/Design/">https://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/wiki/Design/</a> page will still get maintained and improved.... <a class="" href="/p/whonix/featureblog/2013/03/in-depth-detailed-technical-whonix-design/">read more</a></p></div>
