<div style="margin-bottom: 10px">
  <h3>
    <a href="/p/whonix/featureblog/2013/03/advancend-users-file-transfer-ssh-into-mount-whonix-workstation-on-the-host/">Advancend Users: File Transfer, SSH into, mount Whonix-Workstation on the host</a>
  </h3>
  <div class="markdown_content"><p>Instructions how to SSH into Whonix-Workstation (host -&gt; ssh -&gt; Whonix-Gateway -&gt; ssh -&gt; Whonix-Workstation) have been added. You an use ssh, scp and sshfs, thus mount Whonix-Workstation folders on the host.</p>
<p><a href="https://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/wiki/File%20Transfer/#ssh-into-whonix-workstation">https://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/wiki/File%20Transfer/#ssh-into-whonix-workstation</a></p></div>
  <em class="grid-19">
    Posted by <a href="/u/adrelanos/">
    
  
