  <h3>
    <a href="/p/whonix/featureblog/2013/03/censorship---httpwhonixsourceforgenet-blocked-in-china/">#censorship - http://whonix.sourceforge.net blocked in #China</a>
  </h3>
  <div class="markdown_content"><p>According to @GreatFireChina - <a href="http://whonix.sourceforge.net">http://whonix.sourceforge.net</a> is blocked in China while <a href="http://sourceforge.net">http://sourceforge.net</a> is still reachable.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://en.greatfire.org/whonix.sourceforge.net">https://en.greatfire.org/whonix.sourceforge.net</a></li>
